'''Frank Oz''' (born '''Frank Richard Oznowicz'''<ref name="Reddit">{{Reddit|url=r/IAmA/comments/7o6bxv/im_frank_oz_film_director_and_performer_ask_me|thread=I'm Frank Oz, film director and performer: Ask Me Anything|user=Franz Oz (via [https://www.reddit.com/user/MGT_Team MGT_Team])|date=2018-01-04|archivedate=20221019134032}}</ref> on [[May 25]], [[1940s#1944|1944]] in [[Wikipedia:Hereford|Hereford]], [[Wikipedia:Herefordshire|Herefordshire]], [[Wikipedia:England|England]]<ref name="IGN Part 1" />) is an actor, puppeteer and director, best known as the puppeteer for and original voice of [[Yoda]]. Outside ''Star Wars'', Oz is notable for his work with [[W:c:muppet:Jim Henson|Jim Henson's]] Muppets and in film directing.

Although well known for the role of Yoda, Oz refuses to attend fan conventions or imitate the character's voice outside ''Star Wars'', out of his respect for the role.<ref name="aicn">{{WebCite|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/?q=node/33610|text=Capone With Frank Oz About DEATH AT A FUNERAL, What Went Wrong On STEPFORD, And (Of Course) Yoda!!|author="Capone"|archivedate=20070811220629}}</ref>

